{"tid":645621,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"【認真討論】邊個係恩尼斯達接班人","createTime":"2018-04-28T10:03:36.000Z","updateTime":"2018-04-29T10:20:04.000Z","uid":104096,"like":26,"dislike":30,"uniUserReply":97,"replies":[{"pid":"527edae3b08d60dde6b3c37543da73bebf2be423","tid":645621,"uid":104096,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-28T10:03:36.000Z","msg":"係球壇能夠有小白嘅傳控創造力嘅真係唔多<br />\n而且話得接班就一定係後生同當打<br />\n我個人首選isco<br />\n無論傳控創作力都好好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n可塑性好強，不過最大問題係佢踢皇馬<br />\n好難先會有機會轉會<br />\n另外我覺得verratti華拉堤都可以一戰<br />\n佢控傳好靈活，雖然係巴黎進攻嘅職責唔多<br />\n但佢分波同運球能力我覺得係世界最強果批<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n大家隨便分享<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f81267076a2c935278254561f015b2c27567da97","tid":645621,"uid":4957,"like":9,"dislike":5,"score":4,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-04-28T10:04:18.000Z","msg":"B silva"},{"pid":"6f88b5d92a7418d5218f0a3cbbac298c7e4e5f78","tid":645621,"uid":104096,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"f81267076a2c935278254561f015b2c27567da97","tid":645621,"uid":4957,"like":9,"dislike":5,"score":4,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-04-28T10:04:18.000Z","msg":"B silva"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-28T10:05:34.000Z","msg":"係鏝應該都唔會去疤"},{"pid":"9939b8c02be5949cfdd0fe5375a1142f8cc5289b","tid":645621,"uid":143206,"like":12,"dislike":5,"score":7,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-28T10:07:01.000Z","msg":"軒達臣"},{"pid":"f317bab9cdc1f81c20d8ac53cab4c12228054a9e","tid":645621,"uid":50744,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-28T10:09:24.000Z","msg":"閱讀能力先係重點"},{"pid":"f32afb4b925b70054c7357f5ef8c3291882c5a23","tid":645621,"uid":159086,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"6f88b5d92a7418d5218f0a3cbbac298c7e4e5f78","tid":645621,"uid":104096,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"f81267076a2c935278254561f015b2c27567da97","tid":645621,"uid":4957,"like":9,"dislike":5,"score":4,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-04-28T10:04:18.000Z","ms